survey_response.review_text: I had a splendid experience with Dr Smita Pawar. She explained each and every aspect of the scan and was extremely friendly and made me feel extremely comfortable :)
She explained the things and development of baby very well..and we will be so happy to visit her again in next scan.

She explained everything elaborately and while doing my check up ..she made sure that I feel comfortable and relaxed 

She’s friendly and super amazing!!
Doctor Smita Pawar is just amazing, she is warm and humble in her approach. Wouldn’t want to consult any other doctor after consulting her : )

During my pregnancy for nine months, dr Smita Pawar has done all my scans. We were made to do every single one there was. She was very thorough in her explanations during this time. However I delivered a baby girl. A beautiful baby girl. One week after she was born we found out that she had a heart condition and a MAjOR one. It’s called complete AV Canal defect. **** *** *** ******** ****** *** ** *** ***** **** ** ** ****** I have consulted many many Doctors.* *** *** **** *** ** ** *** *** **** *** ****** ** *** ** *** ***** ** We blindly trust in our doctors cos we believe that thy have our best interest. But no. That’s not the case with this hospital CLoUdNine. And dr Pawar. They charge us over the moon and make us do all of the scans and we are happy to. Cos we want the best for our child but at what cost ?? **** * ****** *** ** ** ****** ** ****** ******* *** ** **** *** ** ** **** ******* *** ***** *** ** ** *** ********* ** ***** ** ******** **** ********* **** * ***** ******** ** *** ***** ** **** *********** **** *** ** **** * ******** It’s not a small thing gone amiss! Today my daughter has undergone a heart surgery and So my point of writing this is that I hope this never happens to any one ever again Doctor SMITA and cloudnine hospItals. ! And parents pls consult at your own risk.
